00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:44.959
And make it your goal to start conversations with those three steps.

00:05:44.959 --> 00:05:51.959
Be friendly, converse naturally, and find the right time to express your faith.

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:57.560
Practice at home, or with a friend, and see for yourself how iron sharpens iron.
